Sending Side:
apt-get install perl
apt-get install libsoap-lite-perl 

The sender also needs the sendSMS.pl script

Recieving Side
sudo apt-get install python-pip
sudo apt-get install python-opencv python-wxgtk2.8 python-matplotlib python-numpy python-serial python-pil libwxgtk2.8-dev libpython2.7-dev
sudo pip install MAVProxy

The receiving side needs to run smsListener2 which will require the Maker Modem API

